cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper presents an unsupervised deep learning approach for inter-modality image registration, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a new comprehensive transformation network, which involves artificial intelligence (AI) techniques. Hence, cs.AI is also a likely category. The experiments involve multi-sequence brain MR data and intra-modality 4D cardiac Cine-MR data, which are related to multimedia (MM) and neural networks (NE) categories. Therefore, cs.MM and cs.NE are also likely categories.
